     H            Y/
     F***************************************************
     F*   INQUIRY OF MODULE FROM ASJ                *
     F*                   AUG/09/02  TCH                *
     F*                                                 *
     F*   SEP/16/02  ADD ORDER#                         *
TCH61F*   2005/04/08  FIRST COLUM FIX                   *
TCHK1F*   2005/12/06  CHG  SELECT ONLY ASJ(0002)        *
TCHK1F*                    REMOVE LOGIC(SEL PRIOR 7 DAYS*
TCHK2F*   2008/01/01  CHG  0002 TO 8990                 *
     F***************************************************
     FGDGPW76 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDS
     FGDGPL17 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDGPL16 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDIPL17 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDIPL16 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDLPL14 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     F**GDGWP76 O   E                    DISK
